Xcode projects are included for the following libraries. The projects were
created following the guidelines in the "UPDATING" document.

FREETYPE
http://www.freetype.org/
Release 2.3.11
http://sourceforge.net/projects/freetype/files/freetype2/2.3.11/freetype-2.3.11.tar.bz2/download

Note: because of FreeType's complex header structure, the project
      has a "Copy Files" phase to include the proper headers.

JPEG
http://www.ijg.org/
Release 7
http://www.ijg.org/files/jpegsrc.v7.tar.gz

MAD
http://www.underbit.com/products/mad/
Release 0.15.1b
http://sourceforge.net/projects/mad/files/libmad/0.15.1b/libmad-0.15.1b.tar.gz/download

Note: mad sets some preprocessor macros on a per-arch basis;
      build_config.sh was modified to write them into config.h.

PNG
http://www.libpng.org/
Release 1.2.40
http://prdownloads.sourceforge.net/libpng/libpng-1.2.40.tar.gz?download

SNDFILE
http://www.mega-nerd.com/libsndfile/
Release 1.0.20
http://www.mega-nerd.com/libsndfile/libsndfile-1.0.20.tar.gz

Note: sndfile.h is also generated dynamically; build_config.sh
      was modified to account for this file.

SPEEX
http://www.speex.org/
Release 1.2rc1
http://downloads.xiph.org/releases/speex/speex-1.2rc1.tar.gz

-----

Aleph One also uses the following libraries, which provide an official
framework binary or Xcode project file:

OGG
http://www.xiph.org/ogg/
Release 1.1.4
http://downloads.xiph.org/releases/ogg/libogg-1.1.4.tar.gz

Source only; Xcode project file is located in macosx/Ogg.xcodeproj

Note: Change "C/C++ Compiler Version" to "GCC 4.0"
      Change "Installation Directory" to "@executable_path/../Frameworks"

SDL
http://www.libsdl.org/
Release 1.2.14
http://www.libsdl.org/release/SDL-1.2.14.dmg

SDL_IMAGE
http://www.libsdl.org/projects/SDL_image/
Release 1.2.10
http://www.libsdl.org/projects/SDL_image/release/SDL_image-1.2.10.dmg

SDL_NET
http://www.libsdl.org/projects/SDL_net/
Release 1.2.7
http://www.libsdl.org/projects/SDL_net/release/SDL_net-1.2.7.dmg

SDL_TTF
http://www.libsdl.org/projects/SDL_ttf/
Revision 5226 of SVN trunk
http://svn.libsdl.org/trunk/SDL_ttf

Source only; Xcode project file is inside Xcode.tar.gz

Note: Change "Architectures" to "32-bit Universal"
      Change "C/C++ Compiler Version" to "GCC 4.0"
      Remove "Other Linker Flags"
      Change "Header Search Paths" to remove /usr/X11R6/include entries
      Change "Header Search Paths" to add "/Library/Frameworks/freetype.framework/Headers"
      Remove "Library Search Paths"
      Add freetype.framework to Frameworks section
      
SMPEG
http://icculus.org/smpeg/
Revision 389 of SVN trunk
svn://svn.icculus.org/smpeg/trunk

Source only; Xcode project file is inside Xcode.tar.gz

Note: Change "Architectures" to "32-bit Universal"

VORBIS
http://www.vorbis.com/
Release 1.2.3
http://downloads.xiph.org/releases/vorbis/libvorbis-1.2.3.tar.gz

Source only; Xcode project file is located in macosx/Vorbis.xcodeproj

Note: Change "C/C++ Compiler Version" to "GCC 4.0"
      Change "Installation Directory" to "@executable_path/../Frameworks"

